sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client
    participant TcpServer
    participant TcpConnection
    participant EventLoop
    participant EpollPoller
    participant Buffer as Buffer(inputBuf)
    participant Codec as JsonRpcCodec
    participant Dispatcher
    participant ToolManager
    participant Tool as ReadFileTool
    participant ThreadPool

    Note over Client,Tool: ========== 连接建立阶段 ==========

    Client->>TcpServer: TCP SYN → connect()
    TcpServer->>TcpServer: acceptor_.accept()
    TcpServer->>TcpConnection: new TcpConnection(loop, fd, localAddr, peerAddr)
    TcpConnection->>TcpConnection: socket_ = Socket(fd)
    TcpConnection->>TcpConnection: channel_ = Channel(loop, fd)
    TcpConnection->>EventLoop: channel_->enableReading()
    EventLoop->>EpollPoller: updateChannel(channel_)
    EpollPoller->>EpollPoller: epoll_ctl(EPOLL_CTL_ADD, fd, EPOLLIN|EPOLLET)

    Note over Client,Tool: ========== 数据到达阶段（EPOLLIN 触发） ==========

    Client->>TcpServer: 发送 JSON-RPC Request (TCP send)
    Note right of Client: Content-Length: 128\r\n\r\n{...}
    EpollPoller->>EventLoop: epoll_wait() 返回 active channels
    EventLoop->>EventLoop: 遍历 activeChannels
    EventLoop->>Channel: channel->handleEvent()
    Channel->>TcpConnection: readCallback_()
    TcpConnection->>TcpConnection: handleRead()

    Note over TcpConnection,Buffer: 读取原始数据到 inputBuf
    TcpConnection->>Buffer: inputBuf_.readFd(fd)
    Buffer-->>TcpConnection: 读取 n 字节

    Note over TcpConnection,Codec: 尝试解码（处理粘包/半包）
    TcpConnection->>Codec: codec_->decode(&inputBuf_)
    Codec->>Buffer: findCRLF() 查找 Content-Length 头
    Buffer-->>Codec: 返回 Content-Length 值 = 128
    Codec->>Buffer: 检查 readableBytes() >= 128
    alt 半包：数据不完整
        Codec-->>TcpConnection: return std::nullopt
        Note over TcpConnection: 等待更多数据，继续 epoll_wait
    else 数据完整
        Codec->>Buffer: retrieve(128 + headerLen)
        Codec->>Codec: nlohmann::json::parse(payload)
        Codec->>Codec: 验证 JSON-RPC 2.0 格式
        Codec->>Codec: 构造 Request 结构体
        Codec-->>TcpConnection: return Message(Request)
    end

    Note over TcpConnection,Dispatcher: 分发消息

    TcpConnection->>TcpServer: messageCallback_(conn, message)
    TcpServer->>TcpServer: onMessage(conn, message)

    alt 方法 == "tools/list"
        TcpServer->>Dispatcher: dispatch(request)
        Dispatcher->>ToolManager: listTools()
        ToolManager-->>Dispatcher: vector<ToolInfo>
        Dispatcher->>Dispatcher: 构造 Response (result = tools list)
    else 方法 == "tools/call"
        TcpServer->>Dispatcher: dispatch(request)
        Dispatcher->>Dispatcher: 从 params 提取 tool name + arguments
        Dispatcher->>ToolManager: getTool("read_file")
        ToolManager-->>Dispatcher: Tool* (ReadFileTool instance)

        opt P1: 异步执行（ThreadPool）
            Dispatcher->>ThreadPool: enqueue(Tool::execute, params, ctx)
            ThreadPool->>Tool: execute(params, ctx)
        end

        P0: 同步执行
        Dispatcher->>Tool: execute(params, context)
        Tool->>Tool: validatePath(params["path"])
        alt path 合法
            Tool->>Tool: std::ifstream 读取文件
            Tool-->>Dispatcher: Result::ok(fileContent)
        else path 非法
            Tool-->>Dispatcher: Result::err("Path not allowed")
        else 文件不存在
            Tool-->>Dispatcher: Result::err("File not found")
        end

        Dispatcher->>Dispatcher: 构造 Response
    else 方法不存在
        Dispatcher->>Dispatcher: 构造 Error Response (-32601 Method not found)
    end

    Dispatcher-->>TcpServer: Response

    Note over TcpConnection,Codec: 编码响应

    TcpServer->>TcpConnection: send(response)
    TcpConnection->>Codec: codec_->encode(response)
    Codec->>Codec: response.toJson().dump()
    Codec->>Codec: 拼接 "Content-Length: N\r\n\r\n" + json
    Codec-->>TcpConnection: string (完整响应)

    Note over TcpConnection,Buffer: 写入 outputBuf 并注册写事件

    TcpConnection->>Buffer: outputBuf_.append(encodedResponse)
    TcpConnection->>EventLoop: channel_->enableWriting()
    EventLoop->>EpollPoller: epoll_ctl(EPOLL_CTL_MOD, fd, EPOLLIN|EPOLLOUT|EPOLLET)

    Note over Client,Tool: ========== 数据发送阶段（EPOLLOUT 触发） ==========

    EpollPoller->>EventLoop: epoll_wait() 返回 EPOLLOUT
    EventLoop->>Channel: channel->handleEvent()
    Channel->>TcpConnection: writeCallback_()
    TcpConnection->>TcpConnection: handleWrite()
    TcpConnection->>Buffer: outputBuf_.writeFd(fd)
    Note over Buffer: send() 发送 n 字节
    alt 全部发送完毕
        TcpConnection->>EventLoop: channel_->disableWriting()
        TcpConnection->>Buffer: outputBuf_.retrieveAll()
    else 部分发送
        Note over TcpConnection: 保留剩余数据，等待下次 EPOLLOUT
    end

    Client->>Client: 收到 TCP Response
    Note right of Client: Content-Length: ...\r\n\r\n{"jsonrpc":"2.0","result":{...},"id":1}

    Note over Client,Tool: ========== 连接关闭阶段 ==========

    opt 客户端主动断开
        Client->>TcpServer: TCP FIN
        EpollPoller->>EventLoop: epoll_wait() 返回 EPOLLHUP
        EventLoop->>Channel: channel->handleEvent()
        Channel->>TcpConnection: closeCallback_()
        TcpConnection->>TcpConnection: handleClose()
        TcpConnection->>EventLoop: channel_->disableAll()
        TcpConnection->>EventLoop: loop_->removeChannel(channel_)
        TcpConnection->>Socket: socket_.close()
        TcpServer->>TcpServer: connections_.erase(connName)
    end
